<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>fwq ạlṣlyb mnẓr ʿjyb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- fwq ạlṣlyb mnẓr ʿjyb wạldm nạzf fwq ạlṣlyb
 lyh yạ ḥbyb wạldyn rhyb tḥml ʿqạby lyh yạ ḥbyb
 ạlqrạr - yạ ạbrʿ jmạl fwq ạlṣlyb lạ ṣwrh lyk wlạ jmạl
 fyn ạljmạl fy ạnạ ạ̹zạy ạnạ
 2- ạ̉nạ ạlạ̉tẖym dẖnby ʿẓym wqlby kẖạdʿ wạnt ạlrḥym
 ḥbk ḥmym dmk krym wạlṣlb qạsy wạlmwt ạlym</lyrics>
<author>bhjt ʿdly, bhjt ʿdly</author>
<hymn_number>2704</hymn_number>
</song>